      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the color}}
{{sprotected2}}
{{infobox color
|textcolor     = white
|title         = Black
|pic           =File:Solid_black.svg
|hex           = 000000
|symbolism     = [[darkness]], [[secrecy]], [[Power (philosophy)|power]], [[nubian people|nubian]], [[Esotericism|mystery]]; [[silence]] and [[wikt:hiding|concealment]]; [[death]] (including [[Capital punishment|execution]]) and bereavement; [[Fear]], [[antagonist]], [[wikt:strong|strong]], (with orange) [[Halloween]]; [[wikt:end|end]], [[chaos]], and [[wikt:lack|lack]]; [[evil]], [[Luck|bad luck]], and [[crime]]; conversely, [[elegance]], [[anarchy]], [[Rebellion]], Non-Conformity, [[Individuality]], [[Solidarity]]
|r             = 0
