* [http://www.savingbletchleypark.org/ Saving Bletchley Park] blog by [[Sue Black (computer scientist)|Sue Black]]
* [http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/fac/soc/pais/staff/aldrich/vigilant/lectures/gchq GCHQ: Britain's Most Secret Intelligence Agency]
* [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fKQYECYJEH0 19 minute Video interview] with [[Sue Black (computer scientist)|Sue Black]] by [[Robert Llewellyn]] about Bletchley Park

