*'''タピオカドリンク''' ([[Japanese language|Japanese]]): transliterated ''tapiokadorinku'' translated &quot;tapioca drink&quot;
*'''Trà sữa trân châu''' ([[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]]): literally &quot;pearl milk tea&quot;
*'''ชาไข่มุก, ชานมไข่มุก''' ([[Thai language|Thai]]): literally &quot;tapioca or pearl tea&quot;
*'''Ságo at Guláman''' ([[Tagalog language|Tagalog]]): literally &quot;tapioca pearls and agar&quot;
*'''Teh Mutiara''' ([[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]): literally &quot;pearl tea&quot;
*'''Té de burbujas''' ([[Spanish language|Spanish]]): translated &quot;tea of bubbles&quot;
*'''Suco de Pobá''' ([[Brazilian Portuguese language|Portuguese]]): transliterated &quot;boba juice&quot; from interpretation of boba
*'''Thé aux perles''' ([[French language|French]]): literally &quot;tea with pearls&quot;
*'''តែ​គុជ''' ([[Cambodian language|Khmer]]): literally &quot;tapioca pearl tea&quot;

