      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the North American professional baseball hall of fame|the similar institution of Canadian baseball|Canadian Baseball Hall of Fame|the similar institution of Japanese baseball|Japanese Baseball Hall of Fame|the U.S. college version|National College Baseball Hall of Fame}}
{{Infobox Museum
